data.description: Folks!  Here is an opportunity to own a very unique piece of property in the country. It's approximately 5 miles from Lake Palestine & minutes from Tyler.  The house was built in 2010 and sits on 21 acres.  Approximately 1/3 of the property is wooded.  It has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, open concept, vaulted ceilings, with a large covered back patio.  There is a 16x30 shop behind the house. The land is set up to irrigate.  There is an irrigation storage tank and creek fed pond that can be used to irrigate the property.  Possibilities are endless!  Vineyard, orchard, truck garden, blueberries, blackberries, square bales, horses, it's only limited by your imagination.   Call or text if interested!!! MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Jeff 903-646-0269 or Tina 903-658-5964
